{"article_id":"Cjy66RkkVBjAGwZR","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"WASHINGTON ( ) -","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"U.S. Democratic Senator Al Franken announced his resignation on Thursday","depth":9},{"id":2,"text":"after facing a series of sexual misconduct allegations ,","depth":9},{"id":3,"text":"and Republican Representative Trent Franks also said","depth":10},{"id":4,"text":"he was stepping down","depth":10},{"id":5,"text":"as he too was hit with ethics charges .","depth":9},{"id":6,"text":"Franken ,","depth":10},{"id":7,"text":"buffeted for weeks by sexual harassment charges and under pressure from party colleagues ,","depth":10},{"id":8,"text":"said on the Senate floor","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"he would leave in a few weeks ,","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"although he denied some of the allegations against him","depth":10},{"id":11,"text":"and questioned others .","depth":10},{"id":12,"text":"The 66-year-old former comedian from Minnesota had been seen as a rising star in the Democratic Party .","depth":6},{"id":13,"text":"\" I know in my heart","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"that nothing","depth":12},{"id":15,"text":"I ' ve done as a senator","depth":12},{"id":16,"text":"- nothing -","depth":11},{"id":17,"text":"has brought dishonor on this institution , \"","depth":10},{"id":18,"text":"he said .","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"\" Nevertheless , today I am announcing","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"that in the coming weeks , I will be resigning as a member of the United States Senate . \"","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"Hours later , Franks announced his resignation","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"after two former staff members complained about discussions","depth":10},{"id":23,"text":"he had with them","depth":10},{"id":24,"text":"about his efforts","depth":10},{"id":25,"text":"to find a surrogate mother .","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"\" I deeply regret","depth":11},{"id":27,"text":"that my discussion of this option and process in the workplace caused distress , \"","depth":11},{"id":28,"text":"said Franks ,","depth":11},{"id":29,"text":"who was first elected to his Arizona congressional seat in 2002","depth":12},{"id":30,"text":"and is an outspoken opponent of abortion .","depth":12},{"id":31,"text":"Franks said in a statement","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"that he and his wife \" have long struggled with infertility . \"","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"The developments came","depth":6},{"id":34,"text":"with Congress already held in low regard by voters .","depth":7},{"id":35,"text":"According to a /Ipsos poll ,","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"only 20 percent approved of the way","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"Congress was handling its job ,","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"with 70 percent disapproving .","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"In recent weeks , charges of sexual misconduct have taken down prominent people in the worlds of entertainment , media and politics .","depth":6},{"id":40,"text":"It is somewhat rare for members of the Senate or House of Representatives to resign from office ,","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"but veteran Democratic Representative John Conyers also resigned earlier this week amid sexual harassment accusations","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"that he has denied .","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"The House Ethics Committee said on Thursday","depth":12},{"id":44,"text":"it was investigating yet another lawmaker .","depth":12},{"id":45,"text":"Blake Farenthold , a Republican representative from Texas , faces allegations of sexual harassment , discrimination and retaliation","depth":12},{"id":46,"text":"involving a former female staff member .","depth":12},{"id":47,"text":"Franken has the highest profile of the lawmakers","depth":12},{"id":48,"text":"hit by allegations in the past few weeks .","depth":12},{"id":49,"text":"has not independently verified the accusations against Franken , Franks , Conyers or Farenthold .","depth":11},{"id":50,"text":"Franken ' s seat will initially be filled by a Democrat","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"appointed by Minnesota ' s Democratic governor ,","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"meaning the Republicans ' slim majority in the Senate will not change .","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"Allegations","depth":5},{"id":54,"text":"that Franken had groped and tried to kiss women","depth":6},{"id":55,"text":"without their consent","depth":6},{"id":56,"text":"began to surface three weeks ago .","depth":4},{"id":57,"text":"U.S . Senator Al Franken","depth":8},{"id":58,"text":"( D-MN )","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"departs the U.S. Capitol with his wife Franni","depth":7},{"id":60,"text":"after announcing his resignation over allegations of sexual misconduct on Capitol Hill in Washington , U.S.","depth":6},{"id":61,"text":"December 7 , 2017 .","depth":5},{"id":62,"text":"/Yuri Gripas","depth":4},{"id":63,"text":"He initially said","depth":7},{"id":64,"text":"he was embarrassed and ashamed by his behavior","depth":8},{"id":65,"text":"but would not resign .","depth":8},{"id":66,"text":"But the majority of his Democratic colleagues in the Senate called on Wednesday for his resignation","depth":7},{"id":67,"text":"after a new allegation ,","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"denied by Franken ,","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"hit the news .","depth":8},{"id":70,"text":"\" Some of the allegations against me are simply not true .","depth":7},{"id":71,"text":"Others I remember very differently , \"","depth":7},{"id":72,"text":"Franken said on Thursday .","depth":6},{"id":73,"text":"Striking a tone of defiance ,","depth":8},{"id":74,"text":"he also sought to contrast himself with two prominent Republicans","depth":9},{"id":75,"text":"- President Donald Trump and Senate candidate Roy Moore .","depth":9},{"id":76,"text":"\" I , of all people , am aware","depth":9},{"id":77,"text":"that there is some irony in the fact","depth":11},{"id":78,"text":"that I am leaving","depth":11},{"id":79,"text":"while a man","depth":13},{"id":80,"text":"who has bragged on tape about his history of sexual assault","depth":13},{"id":81,"text":"sits in the Oval Office","depth":12},{"id":82,"text":"and a man","depth":13},{"id":83,"text":"who has repeatedly preyed on young girls","depth":13},{"id":84,"text":"campaigns for the Senate , with the full support of his party , \"","depth":12},{"id":85,"text":"he said .","depth":8},{"id":86,"text":"Trump was heard bragging about kissing and forcibly touching women in a 2005 videotape","depth":10},{"id":87,"text":"that surfaced last year","depth":10},{"id":88,"text":"as he was running for the White House .","depth":9},{"id":89,"text":"He apologized for the remarks ,","depth":9},{"id":90,"text":"but called them private \" locker-room talk \"","depth":10},{"id":91,"text":"and said","depth":11},{"id":92,"text":"he had not done the things","depth":12},{"id":93,"text":"he talked about .","depth":12},{"id":94,"text":"Trump also denied allegations at that time by at least 12 women of sexual advances and groping in the past .","depth":7},{"id":95,"text":"Moore ,","depth":9},{"id":96,"text":"who is running for the Senate in Alabama in a special election on Tuesday ,","depth":9},{"id":97,"text":"has been accused by several women of sexual assault or misconduct","depth":10},{"id":98,"text":"when they were teenagers","depth":10},{"id":99,"text":"and Moore was in his early 30s .","depth":9},{"id":100,"text":"Moore , 70 , has denied the accusations ,","depth":8},{"id":101,"text":"which has not independently verified .","depth":8},{"id":102,"text":"Trump has backed Moore ,","depth":9},{"id":103,"text":"but Senate Republicans have been cooler toward his candidacy .","depth":9},{"id":104,"text":"In pressing Franken to step aside ,","depth":11},{"id":105,"text":"Democrats have tried to capture the moral high ground","depth":12},{"id":106,"text":"and draw a distinction between their party and Republicans .","depth":12},{"id":107,"text":"\" In every workplace in America ,","depth":13},{"id":108,"text":"including the U.S. Senate ,","depth":13},{"id":109,"text":"we must confront the challenges of harassment and misconduct , \"","depth":12},{"id":110,"text":"said Amy Klobuchar , Franken ' s fellow Democratic senator from Minnesota .","depth":11},{"id":111,"text":"Similarly , House Republican Speaker Paul Ryan said on Thursday","depth":10},{"id":112,"text":"he had told Franks","depth":11},{"id":113,"text":"that he should resign .","depth":11},{"id":114,"text":"A special election will be scheduled","depth":11},{"id":115,"text":"to determine a replacement for Franks .","depth":11},{"id":116,"text":"While a Democrat will be appointed initially","depth":13},{"id":117,"text":"to replace Franken ,","depth":13},{"id":118,"text":"his departure could complicate the party ' s efforts","depth":13},{"id":119,"text":"to maintain or build on the 46 Senate seats","depth":14},{"id":120,"text":"they hold .","depth":14},{"id":121,"text":"Two independent senators also vote with the Democrats .","depth":11},{"id":122,"text":"Republicans are defending eight seats in the congressional elections in November 2018","depth":10},{"id":123,"text":"but Democrats will be defending 26","depth":11},{"id":124,"text":"if Minnesota holds a special election for Franken ' s seat .","depth":11},{"id":125,"text":"The election","depth":11},{"id":126,"text":"to fill Franken ' s seat","depth":11},{"id":127,"text":"could be close .","depth":10},{"id":128,"text":"When he ran in 2008 ,","depth":11},{"id":129,"text":"the race was decided after an extensive recount ,","depth":12},{"id":130,"text":"with Minnesota ' s Supreme Court weighing in .","depth":12},{"id":131,"text":"In the 2016 presidential election , Democrat Hillary Clinton won the state by less than 2 percentage points .","depth":10}],"relations":[{"parent":263,"left":0,"right":262,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":262,"left":187,"right":261,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":187,"left":183,"right":186,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":183,"left":163,"right":182,"relati